                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Eddy</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-10-23">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 23, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Adee states that $2,000 additional have been received, making a total of
                    $66,000 available for the ransom of Miss Stone.)</p>
            </div>
